# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Types: feat, fix, refactor, docs, test, ci, chore, style, perf
# Scope: agent, ui, api, config, rag, models, mcp, tools, session
#
# Examples:
#   feat(agent): add Qwen3.5 multimodal support
#   fix(rag): prevent OOM during hierarchical chunking
#   refactor(ui): decompose app.py into modules
#   test(session): add persistence roundtrip tests
#   ci: add ruff linting to GitHub Actions
#   docs: update README with Docker instructions
